{"tid":1711338,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"馬錦燦要你班廢青死都要死返學","createTime":"2019-11-12T11:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T06:19:54.000Z","uid":4587,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3cfd5df1772ee19e1a6a028246662a667cc40d4d","tid":1711338,"uid":4587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cffm3J2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCffm3J2.jpg&h=95cf9504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯和墟馬錦燦中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幫幫手send email!</span></span><br />\ninfo@bmkc.edu.hk<br />\n<br />\n佛教馬錦燦紀念英文中學校長方奕亮先生：<br />\n<br />\n  現時社會氣氛緊張，近日各區都有示威行動，同時警方亦多次未能照顧到學生以及途人的安全。基於校方對同學的不信任，並認為同學濫用豁免基制。校方在下午發布的有關因特別交通情況而缺課的注意事項中提及要求居於北區的學生，即使因堵路或沒有公共交通工具返校，也要透過步行回校，這罔顧學生安全的做法，屬實不安全。步行回校的路線圖中有不少地方均屬於近日北區堵路及警方戒備的路線<br />\n，因此本人為了回應校方對同學的不信任以及罔顧學生安全的決定，決定將學校列為無法確保本人安全的地方。並決定再三審視每朝回校的決定，以策自身安全。更希望校方能夠撤回此規定，為保障學生安全。"},{"pid":"0072ac1baa1cd3a6c844811f22640dae79677f29","tid":1711338,"uid":4587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01700fa055e849b3d5a19f09074e0e06261da532","tid":1711338,"uid":4587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"北區幾間學校停課, 馬綿燦校長仲屌你班人唔返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43910e616a653accc7dec3334c9b946dae1bc4e4","tid":1711338,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:15:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾學校，5個banding年代band2頭，宜家得返band3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},